MAC

桌面建立Django資料夾
開啟DOS
輸入 
cd desktop cd Django
python -m venv venv
cd venv

source bin/activate
pip install django(安裝最新版本）

安裝後輸入
python
import django
django.VERSION

在VENV路徑輸入
django-admin.py start project mysite
cd mystie


python manage.py runserver -h (可以看help指令）
python manage.py runserver

開啟chrome
輸入http://127.0.0.1:8000/
或
輸入http://localhost:8000/


修改desktop/django/VENV/mysite/foods/views.py

from django.shortcuts import render

# Create your views here.
from django.http import HttpResponse

def hello_world(request):
	return HttpResponse("Hello World!")



修改desktop/django/VENV/mysite/mysite/urls.py

from foods.views import hello_world
from django.conf.urls import url

urlpatterns = [
    url(r'^hello/$', hello_world),
]

chrome URL:http://localhost:8000/hello/
